OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FDry with any early morning
OL,6,Fcloud soon burning off to leave a very
OL,7,Fwarm or hot day with good spells of
OL,8,Fhazy sunshine. Fresher around some
OL,9,Fcoasts with seas breezes developing.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FA fine end to the day with
OL,12,Fhazy sunshine and staying dry
OL,13,Fovernight with variable cloud cover.
OL,14,FWinds will be light.
OL,15,
OL,16,CThursday:FMainly dry and bright with
OL,17,Fhazy sunshine and very warm or hot.
OL,18,FLight winds with sea breezes. Isolated
OL,19,Fheavy showers possible in the evening.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
